{"tid":2156018,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐軍放演習片 專家︰做給美國看","createTime":"2020-08-14T07:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T07:24:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84073b00557d30850176cc585e87352b6787bb67","tid":2156018,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/WNICDD3SIFDTHHGB7XUSG5F6ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FWNICDD3SIFDTHHGB7XUSG5F6ZU%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcVCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=3f728def\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FWNICDD3SIFDTHHGB7XUSG5F6ZU%2F&h=1693de04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/WNICDD3SIFDTHHGB7XUSG5F6ZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n駐軍放演習片 專家︰做給美國看<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ITSZeOJ7j52HFGqXcsdAvPtaql4=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NYOGGCSG2FDDVK7VN37CPYZ52Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FITSZeOJ7j52HFGqXcsdAvPtaql4%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNYOGGCSG2FDDVK7VN37CPYZ52Y.jpg&h=b11bb1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃東<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港是中美冷戰的前緣和磨心，解放軍駐港部隊近日在內地社交網站上載影片，大騷航空兵團防空演習成果，既有導彈試射，又有火炮射擊，向外示強。軍事評論員黃東對本報表示，片段明顯是做給美國看，「如果你飛埋嚟香港，我都唔會手軟」。<br />\n<br />\n這片段僅長48秒，除了開始數個鏡頭疑是駐港部隊在港的軍營及落馬洲口岸外，其餘鏡頭均是在西北地區、滿佈風力發電設施的戈壁灘上拍攝。片段是展示航空兵團防空營的訓練成果，鏡頭顯示速射炮密集發射，官兵演練發射導彈。短片最後，駐港部隊的防空營展示他們的徽號，其中香港的英文是用「Hong Kong」，而不是用普通話拼音「Xiāng gǎng」。<br />\n<br />\n黃東指出，駐港部隊此次上載短片意涵明顯：「毫無疑問係做畀美國睇，做畀香港藍絲睇！」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃東又表示，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d732580b8a60098b5499d7135ffa7222cfb2e145","tid":2156018,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/Gtx0FQLYyoPU0mNAMQtC7lHqlE5FsCjt-OVHASJh6FsvYWOnGtnC9bLYqpCly_aPhx_LyGzpy_1ofJhppfOHaw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FGtx0FQLYyoPU0mNAMQtC7lHqlE5FsCjt-OVHASJh6FsvYWOnGtnC9bLYqpCly_aPhx_LyGzpy_1ofJhppfOHaw&h=817fb97d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}